{"@context": "http://schema.org", "@type": "Movie", "url": "/title/tt0097441/", "name": "Glory", "image": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODhlNjA5MDEtZDVhNS00ZmM3LTg1YzAtZGRjNjhjNTAzNzVkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjUwMzI2NzU@._V1_.jpg", "genre": ["Biography", "Drama", "History", "War"], "contentRating": "R", "actor": [{"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0000111/", "name": "Matthew Broderick"}, {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0000243/", "name": "Denzel Washington"}, {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0000144/", "name": "Cary Elwes"}, {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0000151/", "name": "Morgan Freeman"}], "director": {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0001880/", "name": "Edward Zwick"}, "creator": [{"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0418883/", "name": "Kevin Jarre"}, {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0457016/", "name": "Lincoln Kirstein"}, {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0120837/", "name": "Peter Burchard"}, {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0789946/", "name": "Robert Gould Shaw"}, {"@type": "Organization", "url": "/company/co0005883/"}, {"@type": "Organization", "url": "/company/co0174838/"}], "description": "Glory is a movie starring Matthew Broderick, Denzel Washington, and Cary Elwes. Robert Gould Shaw leads the U.S. Civil War's first all-black volunteer company, fighting prejudices from both his own Union Army, and the Confederates.", "datePublished": "1990-01-18", "keywords": "19th century,american civil war,black soldier,military uniform,soldier", "aggregateRating": {"@type": "AggregateRating", "ratingCount": 124144, "bestRating": "10.0", "worstRating": "1.0", "ratingValue": "7.8"}, "review": {"@type": "Review", "itemReviewed": {"@type": "CreativeWork", "url": "/title/tt0097441/"}, "author": {"@type": "Person", "name": "FrankBooth_DeLarge"}, "dateCreated": "2005-02-01", "inLanguage": "English", "name": "The Best Civil War Movie I've Ever Seen", "reviewBody": "If you think about it, most war movies are about WWII and there aren't as many movies about the Civil War. I haven't seen Gettysburg, but I did see Gods and Generals, and believe me that wasn't all that great. The best Civil War movie I've ever seen is Glory. The movie has an excellent cast which includes Mathew Broderick(only three years after he was in Ferris Buellers Day Off), Denzel Washington, and Morgan Freeman.\n\nI first saw this in my eight grade history class when we were learning about the Civil War. This movie has a great score and it really captures the feel of the Civil War through its battle scenes. For those of you who only watch war movies to see people getting their heads blown off, this is the wrong movie for you. This movie focuses on the characters and what they're going through. Despite having a long running time, the result of this movie is an entertaining and well made war movie.\n\nYou should only buy this movie if you really like it, because it gets a little bit slow the second time you see it. Either way, I'd say you should watch this movie to see what quality war films are all about.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "worstRating": "1", "bestRating": "10", "ratingValue": "9"}}, "duration": "PT2H2M", "trailer": {"@type": "VideoObject", "name": "Glory", "embedUrl": "/video/imdb/vi732561689", "thumbnail": {"@type": "ImageObject", "contentUrl": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BM2IyMDJkY2EtYjg0MS00ZWYyLWJjYTYtMTQ0YmQ5MjBhN2ViXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzU1NzE3NTg@._V1_.jpg"}, "thumbnailUrl": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BM2IyMDJkY2EtYjg0MS00ZWYyLWJjYTYtMTQ0YmQ5MjBhN2ViXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzU1NzE3NTg@._V1_.jpg", "description": "Home Video Trailer from Columbia Tristar", "uploadDate": "2008-04-11T14:17:20Z"}, "cast_and_character": [{"actor": {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0000111/?ref_=tt_cl_t1", "name": "Matthew Broderick"}, "character_and_episodes": [{"url": "/title/tt0097441/characters/nm0000111?ref_=tt_cl_t1", "name": "Col. Robert Gould Shaw"}]}, {"actor": {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0000144/?ref_=tt_cl_t3